Config
	- put all config in a config module
	- use env variables

Relationships:


- A user can have many orders (one-to-many).
- An order belongs to one user (many-to-one).
- A product belongs to one category (many-to-one).
- A category can have many products (one-to-many).
- A product can have many variants (one-to-many).
- A product variant belongs to one product (many-to-one).
- An order can have many order items (one-to-many).
- An order item belongs to one order (many-to-one).
- An order item references a product variant (many-to-one).
- A payment belongs to one order (many-to-one).

This design supports products with categories and variants, allowing for flexible product options (such as size or color) and accurate inventory tracking.

Let me know if you have any questions or if you'd like me to elaborate on any part of the design!

